summary: An ordinance relating to portions of Lots 9, 10, 11 and 12, Hasslocher's Addition to West Seattle and portions of Puget Boulevard acquired by the Federal Public Housing Authority by condemnation, Civil Docket No. 678, United States District Court; and authorizing the acceptance by the City of an "Agreement for Termination of Exclusive Use," thereof.
